s Information System, Ministry of Energy and Mines (Ontario). Retrieved 2012-03-26.", "title": "Temagami-Lorrain Mine"}], "error": null, "wall_time_ms": 1776.04232900012, "model_target": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "model_draft": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct", "seed": 42, "__kind__": "step"}
